list.abstract: art（Algebra Reconstruction Technique）是英文简写，代数重建法的意思。用于两种经典迭代格式的修正。

yingyinNormal.en: It's not food, it's art.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是食物，这是艺术品。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I saw you working on your art project.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可是我看到你做你的艺术课项目了。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, on the bright side, you've invented window art.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，往好的方面想， 你发明了窗户艺术。

yingyinNormal.en: Your mother's photos are important works of art, Erik.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你母亲拍摄的照片是珍贵的艺术品，埃里克。

yingyinNormal.en: You're in a work of art. I think a lot of people would love to be in a work of art.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的形象出现在一幅艺术品里，我觉得很多人都会喜欢出现在艺术作品中。

yingyinNormal.en: She spent three hundred dollars on art supplies. You're not an artist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她花了三百块买艺术用品。你又不是艺术家。

yingyinNormal.en: Of a naked photo of my client. Renowned piece of art.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那可是我当事人的裸照。是一幅著名艺术品。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you know what I used to do before I had you? Art. I wanted to be an artist when I grew up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道我生你之前是做什么的吗？搞艺术的。我小时候的理想是当一名艺术家。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me. I've been to the art section of Bed, Bath & Beyond.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不好意思，我倒是去过家居店的艺术品区。

yingyinNormal.en: Nowadays, much of this art is available for everyone to enjoy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 时至今日，园内有很多艺术巨作供大家欣赏。

yingyinNormal.en: Fair enough, but in its essence, teaching is a performance art.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，但是从本质上来讲教书是一门表演艺术。

yingyinNormal.en: The promenade is home to some of the territories premier arts institutions, like the Museum of Art and the Hong Kong Cultural Centre.
yingyinNormal.zh: 海滨公园是一些顶级艺术馆的所在地，当中包括香港艺术馆和香港文化中心。

yingyinNormal.en: The theater is a temple of art. A precious cornucopia of creative energy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 剧场是艺术的殿堂，剧场能孕育出珍贵的创造力。

yingyinNormal.en: Folding is a real art. The more folds, the better the dim sum chef.
yingyinNormal.zh: 包饺子是一种真正的艺术，折皱包得越多的点心师傅就越好。

yingyinNormal.en: Just a short stroll away is the world's greatest treasure-house of art, the Musee du Louvre.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再散步一小段路，眼前就是世界上最伟大的艺术宝藏，卢浮宫。

yingyinNormal.en: You had time to finish your little art project, but you didn't have time to finish your chores?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有时间完成你那个小艺术品，但是却没有时间做完家务吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, but I've got tickets to the Van Gogh exhibit. I've been waiting like a year for this. Art lover.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也买了梵高画展的票，我盼了一年才盼到。艺术爱好者。

yingyinNormal.en: Or, a guerilla art exhibit in dumbo? Or, hey, isn't the New York film festival still going on?
yingyinNormal.zh: 或者是一场边缘艺术展？还是？对了，纽约电影节还没结束吧？

yingyinNormal.en: What'd you say? I said art lover. Is that supposed to be an insult? I don't know, I'm very tired.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说什么？我说艺术爱好者。那是用来侮辱人的吗？不知道，我很累了。

yingyinNormal.en: I've never seen a gorilla drive a car before, but if you put it in a museum, I'm not gonna call it art.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没见过猩猩开车，但这也不说明把它放在博物馆里就能变成艺术品。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The really successful holders of such titles are those that bring in high-profile <highlight>arts</highlight> events and good press for a year.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些头衔的获得者中真正成功的是这样一群人，他们带来了一整年知名度高的艺术活动以及高质量的新闻报道。

examination_example.sentence: Yet children appear to have it down to an <highlight>art</highlight> — and for the most part they don't need self-help books or therapy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，孩子们似乎已经把它归结为一门艺术，在大多数情况下，他们不需要自助书籍或治疗。

examination_example.sentence: The British land <highlight>art</highlight>, typified by Richard Long's piece, was not only more domestically scaled, but a lot quirkier than its American counterpart.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 以朗的作品为代表的英国地景艺术不仅在国内，而且比美国的同类作品要古怪得多。

examination_example.sentence: Some artists seem to worry about in the <highlight>art</highlight>-science partnership their role may be underestimated.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一些艺术家似乎担心，在艺术与科学的合作中，他们的作用可能被低估了。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Art</highlight>-science collaborations have received favorable responses.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 艺术与科学的合作得到了良好的回应。

examination_example.sentence: "The Heart of the Matter," the just-released report by the American Academy of <highlight>Arts</highlight> and Sciences, deserves praise.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国文理科学院刚刚发布的报告《问题的核心》值得称赞。

sense_info_list.en: skill that comes through experience or study

examination_example.sentence: There are a number of approaches to mastering the <highlight>art</highlight> of deep work.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 掌握深层技艺有很多方法。

examination_example.sentence: The key to mastering the <highlight>art</highlight> of deep work keep to your focus time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 掌握深度工作技术的关键是保持你专注的时间。

word_usage.usage: art的复数形式arts有“文科”之意，the fine arts则通常指美术，包括油画、图画、雕刻、建筑等，有时也包括舞蹈、戏剧、音乐。
art除了“艺术”之外，还有“技术，技巧”的意思，可以用have/get sth. down to a fine art表示“出色完成某事”。
